rene Kray i kommende storfilmer. Forh\u00e5pentligvis vil han fortsette \u00e5 skinne i mindre, skuespillerdrevne filmer som denne. Den dramatiske sluttscenen, som hele filmen bygger opp mot, er s\u00e5 bra skrevet, spilt og regissert at det f\u00e5r \u00abThe Drop\u00bb til \u00e5 gl\u00f8de som en enda bedre film enn den ellers kanskje, strengt tatt, er."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1b682da9046a5e0c1061813f4a33cc15349ae93af4197edd5f42ec86f0eac048"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-04T08:53:00.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Tom Hardy er s\u00e5 god som bartender i mafiaskvis at solid B-film blir sv\u00e6rt severdig."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article10740760.ece/awp1nq/ALTERNATES/w980-default/TheDrop.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5ec1d5478f00282a28f80ae2ad4c0e905ac60aaa.jpg?59743a98"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Str\u00e5lende Hardy -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "5ec1d5478f00282a28f80ae2ad4c0e905ac60aaa"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "film"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["killing them softly", "the drop", "andrerw dominiks", "noomi rapace", "micha\u00ebl r. roskam", "bullhead", "mad max", "b-film", "kray", "kosmorama"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norden"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["james gandolfini", "matthias schoenaerts", "dennis lehane", "tom hardy"]}, {